00196 void FusionCELDataGCOSTest::CompareHeaderData()
00197 {
00198         // Check all header values
00199         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetVersion() == gcosCel->GetVersion());
00200         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetCols() == gcosCel->GetCols());
00201         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetRows() == gcosCel->GetRows());
00202         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumCells() == gcosCel->GetNumCells());
00203 
00204         std::string headerString = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetHeader());
00205         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(headerString == gcosCel->GetHeaderString());
00206         std::string algString = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetAlg());
00207         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(algString == gcosCel->GetAlg());
00208         std::string paramString = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetParams());
00209         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(paramString == gcosCel->GetParams());
00210         std::string chipTypetring = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetChipType());
00211         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(chipTypetring == gcosCel->GetChipType());
00212 
00213         std::string params = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetParams());
00214         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel->GetParams() == params);
00215         std::string algorithmParameters = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameters());
00216         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameters() == algorithmParameters);
00217         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters() == gcosCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters());
00218         int paramCount = fusionCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters();
00219         for (int ip = 0; ip < paramCount; ++ip)
00220         {
00221                 std::wstring fusionParamTag = fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(ip);
00222                 std::string gcosParamTag = gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(ip);
00223                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionParamTag) == gcosParamTag);
00224                 std::string fusionParamValue = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameter(fusionParamTag.c_str()));
00225                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionParamValue == gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameter(gcosParamTag.c_str()));
00226         }
00227 
00228         // Test GetParameters
00229         FusionTagValuePairTypeList& calvinList = fusionCel->GetParameters();
00230         int gcosParamCount = gcosCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters();
00231 
00232         std::list<FusionTagValuePairType>::iterator ci = calvinList.begin();
00233 
00234         for (int gi = 0; ci != calvinList.end() && gi < gcosParamCount; ++ci, ++gi)
00235         {
00236                 std::string calvinTag = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(ci->Tag);
00237                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinTag == gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(gi));
00238                 std::string calvinValue = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(ci->Value);
00239                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinValue == gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameter(gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(gi).c_str()));
00240                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ci->Tag == ci->DetailedType().GetName());
00241                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ci->Value == ci->DetailedType().GetValueText());
00242         }
00243 
00244         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetCellMargin() == gcosCel->GetCellMargin());
00245         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumOutliers() == gcosCel->GetNumOutliers());
00246         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumMasked() == gcosCel->GetNumMasked());
00247         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetDatHeader()) == gcosCel->GetDatHeader());
00248         
00249         CompareGridCoordinates();
00250 }

00252 void FusionCELDataGCOSTest::CompareGridCoordinates()
00253 {
00254         // Check the grid
00255         affymetrix_fusion_io::FGridCoords fusionGrid = fusionCel->GetGridCorners();
00256         GridCoordinatesType gcosRect = gcosCel->GetGridCorners();
00257         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.upperleft.x = (float)gcosRect.upperleft.x);
00258         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.upperleft.y = (float)gcosRect.upperleft.y);
00259         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.upperright.x = (float)gcosRect.upperright.x);
00260         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.upperright.y = (float)gcosRect.upperright.y);
00261         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.lowerright.x = (float)gcosRect.lowerright.x);
00262         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.lowerright.y = (float)gcosRect.lowerright.y);
00263         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.lowerleft.x = (float)gcosRect.lowerleft.x);
00264         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.lowerleft.y = (float)gcosRect.lowerleft.y);
00265 }
